pps/986680/extras/3090b6c4fb5e2d8e1b1d41bd123fd03c.mp4?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience 3v1 asymmetrical multiplayer action. Choose your path: play as the righteous Exorcists to banish evil, or unleash your fury as the burgeoning Malevolent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/4cfcfcc1271bbfb71f08753e6e376626.avif?t=1769650121\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Gameplay demonstrating martial arts straight from modern practitioners and masters. State-of-the-art motion capture technology allows players to experience the true power of Taiwanese martial arts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Spells are based on Taoist practices, reproduced digitally under the guidance of Taoist priests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Solve unique puzzles and beat mini-games that combine elements of Taiwanese culture and religion, such as moon blocks and the Tao's divine bagua.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/e9ad6df7e56c1781474150b52e3f0e26.poster.avif?t=1769650121\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/e9ad6df7e56c1781474150b52e3f0e26.webm?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/e9ad6df7e56c1781474150b52e3f0e26.mp4?t=1769650121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Take in a new musical style that merges oriental musical instruments with metal and electronic music. The soundtrack has been professionally produced to induce a movie-like enjoyment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The haunted houses and temples within are real. The production team personally scouted these areas and conducted field investigations, experiencing many \"spiritual phenomena\" along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Support for multiple languages in stories, including Traditional Chinese, English, Japanese, Korean, Russian, French, German, Spanish and Portuguese. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Supports Windows</p>",
